Changes in v0.3

+ Reduced messages, added filtering by loglevel for srv_ctrl image messages
+ [FEATURE] Added script to update CHANGELOG and simplify release process.
+ Temporary files are saved in "temp" subdirectory.
+ Fixed missing region parameter in cfmc_rendermap.bat
+ Added explicit call to stop mc server and save map to cf_delete.
+ Feature: Send mail at start and termination of run-stack.
+ Added index.html example file to link to overviewer generated maps.


v0.2
Added logging to aws cloudwatch.
Removed saving log files to s3.
Fixed missing region parameter bug when downloading remote config from s3.

v0.1
Added setup_shortcuts.bat to create shortcuts for Microsoft Windows.
Created from dos_ec2_docker_minecraft and dos_ctrl_ec2.
